{"tid":2237101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全日空向員工提出自願離職計劃兼取消冬季獎金","createTime":"2020-10-10T04:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T09:30:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b79522bf286f5c9e2f3ca110a39ec8a3f2b43f","tid":2237101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/全日空向員工提出自願離職計劃兼取消冬季獎金-031807719.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%85%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%A9%BA%E5%90%91%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%85%BC%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E5%86%AC%E5%AD%A3%E7%8D%8E%E9%87%91-031807719.html&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=95d27ad0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/全日空向員工提出自願離職計劃兼取消冬季獎金-031807719.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200512/336894177562464256.jpeg/gAbTw05mAyu58jgEcLF9Tq_Jv-Psuds0jkmzSo5Js0o?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200512%2F336894177562464256.jpeg%2FgAbTw05mAyu58jgEcLF9Tq_Jv-Psuds0jkmzSo5Js0o%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=d9e5ab8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本航空公司全日空(ANA)表示，已向工會提出自願離職計劃，以應對疫情爆發導致航空旅遊業近乎中斷的困境。<br />\n<br />\n全日空發言人表示，計劃完全削減冬季獎金並將減薪，強調會就裁員問題與工會展開真誠的討論，同時還將允許員工暫時放長達兩年的無薪假。<br />\n<br />\n據《日經新聞》報道，全日空將簡化國內航班，並縮減辦公規模，作為重組業務的一部分。(mn/k)~"},{"pid":"e96bb9cffbea2f0279b77192ea0fff20c6aad5ab","tid":2237101,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}